<textList name="BS_EVENT_PIRATE_SUICIDE_TEXT">
	<text>As you jump in you register a dreadful looking pirate station. Its hull is reinforced with parts from various ships and the corpses of various species are attached to it as well. They are refusing all hails. Better prepare for the worst.</text>
	<text>After arriving in the system you are hailed: "YOU! We've been... looking... for YOU. Yes, yes exactly for you. Let's get it on!" These guys seem seriously fucked up, but you will have to stay in their range if you want to jump from this beacon.</text>
	<text>You receive confused com chatter from a small pirate station. Various individuals scream into the coms, the voices modified by overlay effects. Strange music plays in the background. You don't understand what they say but they definitely don't seem friendly. After a bit they power up their weapons.</text>
	<text>A station at this beacon messages you: "Greetings! We hate you and will kill you now!"</text>
